             was indicted for <rs id="t18331128-124-off701" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-off701" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-off701" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18331128-124-cd702" type="crimeDate">9th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18331128-124-off701 t18331128-124-cd702"></join>, 1 counterpane, value 5s.; 1 bolster, 4s.; 1 blanket, value 2s., and 1 towel, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18331128-124-victim1294" type="victimName">
                     Sophia Louisa 
                     Lewis
                  <interp inst="t18331128-124-victim1294" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
