                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-person1297" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker. I have a counterpane pawned by the prisoner; I knew her well.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18331128-124-person1298">
                  WILLIAM 
                  COOK
               <interp inst="t18331128-124-person1298" type="surname" value="COOK"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-person1298" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-person1298" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             (police-constable N 96). I was on duty on the 16th of October; the prosecutrix came to me and said she had been robbed, and she gave me these duplicates - I was about a week looking for the prisoner, but could not find her; she then came and gave herself up.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined. Q. Did she say she was ordered to pawn them by the young man? A. No.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The young man ordered me to pawn these things; and when she missed them she said if I would get them back it would do. I pawned them in the name of Marriott, which is my name.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 17. - <rs id="t18331128-124-verdict705" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-verdict705" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-verdict705" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               Recommended to Mercy by the Jury
            </rs>. <rs id="t18331128-124-punish706" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-punish706" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18331128-124-punish706" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18331128-124-defend1292 t18331128-124-punish706"></join>
               Fined 1s.
            </rs> and Discharged.</p>
